Transformation of a String to a Password.

Password should be easy to remember and hard to guess.

One technique is to have a sentence which can be easily remembered transformed to a password. This Module provides a String.to_pwd Method which transforms a sentence to a password.

Currently, the class is only aware of transformations form german phrases

USAGE

irb> "Da steht ein Pferd auf dem Flur".to_pwd
=> "Ds1P@dF"
